    It was not a balloon, but a novelty toy called a dying pig that made an awful sound. Think of something like a woopie cushion but with a different noi<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    It was not a balloon, but a novelty toy called a dying pig that made an awful sound. Think of something like a woopie cushion but with a different noise maker. <br /><a target="_blank" href="http://www.weirduniverse.net/blog/comments/dying_pigs" rel="nofollow noopener">http://www.weirduniverse.net/blog/com...</a><a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
