    <a title="Ruby Granger" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/21679362-ruby-granger"><img alt="Ruby Granger" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1583704350p2/21679362.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
