        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2508884269" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8973262496934271345">This is such a classic Agatha Christie! <br/><br/>A nasty old man, his mostly estranged family bearing many a grudge, brought together with a smattering of servants and unexpected guests for a very dysfunctional Christmas in the family mansion. When the old man inevitably ends up dead and some precious jewels go missing there are any number of suspects for the police and Hercule Poirot to investigate. Of course Monsieur Poirot&apos;s little grey cells will quickly sort out the truth from the lies and secrets a</span>
  <span id="freeText8973262496934271345" style="display:none">This is such a classic Agatha Christie! <br /><br />A nasty old man, his mostly estranged family bearing many a grudge, brought together with a smattering of servants and unexpected guests for a very dysfunctional Christmas in the family mansion. When the old man inevitably ends up dead and some precious jewels go missing there are any number of suspects for the police and Hercule Poirot to investigate. Of course Monsieur Poirot's little grey cells will quickly sort out the truth from the lies and secrets and solve the case.<br /><br />So good to re-visit Agatha Christie from time to time and be reminded of what a consummate story teller she was!</span>
